sYs =
 
   (s+2) (s-1)
  -------------
  (s+3)^2 (s-5)
 
Continuous-time zero/pole/gain model.
Model Properties
>> % dan untuk mengembalikannya ke bentuk polynomial
>> s = tf('s')

s =
 
  s
 
Continuous-time transfer function.
